---

<section class="cta" id="book">
  <div class="cta__inner">
    <h2 class="cta__title">Ready to turn marketing into predictable revenue?</h2>
    <p class="cta__sub">
      30 minutes with Kevin. No pitch deck, no sales rep. We'll look at your account together and tell you — plainly — whether we can help.
    </p>
    <a class="rk-btn rk-btn--teal rk-btn--lg" href="/contact">
      Book Your Free Consultation <span class="rk-btn__arrow">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <div class="cta__meta">
      <span>&#10003; 30 min</span>
      <span>&#10003; Direct with founder</span>
      <span>&#10003; No obligation</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    padding: 64px var(--pad);
    background: var(--paper);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse 50% 50% at 50% 0%,
      var(--teal-50) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
  }
  .cta__inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .cta__title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--ink-900);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .cta__sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink-600);
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
    max-width: 52ch;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta__meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-500);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
